txfixtures (0.5.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version 0.5.1

  * Make txfixtures compatible with twisted 24.x
  * Deprecate using thread.isAlive
  * Drop support for python < 3.8  
  * Temporarily comment out timezone dependent test
  * Add basic GHA configuration
  * Remove obsolete travis configuration
  * txfixtures is compatible with up to twisted version 22.10
  * Restrict maximum supported Twisted version
  * Remove unused code
  * Remove phantom.js fixture
  * Remove support for MongoDB
  * Update obsolete tox configuration
  * Fix mongodb cleanup ordering
  * Handle newer versions of mongodb
  * Add selenium<4 upper bound for phantomjs extra

 -- Tushar Gupta <tushar.gupta@canonical.com>  Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:53:48 +0530

